snippet.title: Exmortis Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Exmortis is a free flash horror game. Check it out here: http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/189227

You wake up in the woods with no memory of how you got there. Nightmares of blood and screams still echo through your mind. It's late and it's cold - unless you can find shelter fast, you won't last the night. You spot a house in a clearing up ahead and left with no choice - you decide to shelter there for the night. Soon after you begin to realise that death is a welcome choice compared to what lies waiting for you inside...

Thanks for watching :)
